lead_paragraph: Roger Federer turned on the style to win 10 of the last 11 points in a 7-6(2) 7-6(1) defeat of Germany's Florian Mayer and reach the semi-finals of the Mercedes Cup in Stuttgart on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Federer Beats Mayer to Reach Semis in Stuttgart
